com.tempodb

Class WritableDataPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tempodb.WritableDataPoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class WritableDataPoint
extends Object
implements Serializable
    DataPoint for a Series, used for bulk writing of DataPoints.

    Allows you to specify a timestamp/value pair, as well as the Series that it is associated with.

    Since:
    1.0.0
